\begin_layout Standard
欧拉转动矩阵的形式为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{U}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
c_{\alpha}c_{\beta}c_{\phi}-s_{\alpha}s_{\phi} & -c_{\alpha}c_{\beta}s_{\phi}-c_{\phi}s_{\alpha} & c_{\alpha}s_{\beta}\\
c_{\beta}c_{\phi}s_{\alpha}+c_{\alpha}s_{\phi} & c_{\alpha}c_{\phi}-c_{\beta}s_{\alpha}s_{\phi} & s_{\alpha}s_{\beta}\\
-c_{\phi}s_{\beta} & s_{\beta}s_{\phi} & c_{\beta}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{U}\left(\alpha,\beta,\phi\right)$
\end_inset

对应的逆矩阵是
\begin_inset Formula $\left(-\phi,-\beta,-\alpha\right)$
\end_inset

。
